    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>SIVIN--Bernard, 81, on April 22, 2007. Treasured husband of Shirley; beloved father of Barbara, Edward, and the late Lois, next to whom he now will rest; grandfather of David, Alana, Kai and Colin; and father-in-law of Maritza and Ronald. Words cannot do him justice.</p>
      </block>
